## 🎨 Customization Tips

### Change Poems
Edit the poems array in `script.js` (lines 14-38):
```javascript
const poems = [
    { title: "Your Title", body: "Your poem text..." },
    // Add more poems here
];
```

### Update Book List
Modify the book cards in `index.html` (around line 330-400).

### Change Colors
Edit the CSS variables at the top of `style.css`:
```css
:root {
    --accent-pink: #ffb7c5;    /* Change pink accent */
    --accent-yellow: #fffdd0;  /* Change yellow */
    /* etc. */
}
```

### Modify Star Information
Update `starData` object in `script.js` (around line 210).

