## 🐛 Troubleshooting

**Music won't play?**
- Check that MP3 files are in the same folder as index.html
- Make sure filenames match exactly: `505.mp3`, `linger.mp3`, `thecure.mp3`
- Try a different browser if it still doesn't work

**Poems not showing?**
- Refresh the page (Ctrl+R or Cmd+R)
- Check browser console (F12) for errors

**Mobile menu not working?**
- Make sure you're in a browser (not PDF viewer)
- Try a different mobile browser
- Clear cache and refresh

**Hamburger menu stuck?**
- Press ESC key to close it
- Click the menu area outside the drawer

